OL,4,G2100FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,5,     GNazi leadership appeared unified,
OL,6,     Gbut behind the scenes, it was
OL,7,     Gmarked by nepotism, corruption,
OL,8,     Gand fear. The hierarchy was
OL,9,     Gambitious, ruthless, and
OL,10,     Gcutthroat, with leaders competing
OL,11,     Gfor power.
OL,12,G2200FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,13,     GIn their pursuit of the Aryan
OL,14,     Gdream, the Nazis were burdened by
OL,15,     Ginternal ideological conflict,
OL,16,     Gwhich undermined their ability to
OL,17,     Gsucceed in WWII and ultimately
OL,18,     Gled to the deaths of millions.
