OL,4,G2300FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,5,     GEarly victories in WWII gave
OL,6,     GHitler a dangerous over-
OL,7,     Gconfidence, which was later
OL,8,     Gtested and proven vulnerable. His
OL,9,     Ghubris and greed ultimately led
OL,10,     Gto Germany's defeat as time
OL,11,     Grevealed his flaws.
